System requirements
    python is installed
    # to install required python packages
    sudo pip install -r requirements.txt

Before first run, do this
    python manage.py migrate

To run the server
    python manage.py runserver 8008

After the server has been been started, the following command can test it.
3 of 4 of the tests should pass (the first test doesn't pass because 
authentication was removed)
    python run_tests.py
